{"tid":849202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[侵侵???] 美國8月貿赤擴至532億美元　大豆出口挫28%","createTime":"2018-10-05T13:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T14:52:45.000Z","uid":147097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"160a4a0b7367993951a0dc6c796df3d29484e417","tid":849202,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:38:27.000Z","msg":"美國商務部公布，8月份貿易赤字擴大6.4%，由7月份的500億美元增至532億美元，創半年新高，但略低過市場預期536億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n期內整體出口跌0.8%至2,094.3億美元，當中大豆出口減少28%至25.8億美元，而整體入口則增加0.6%至2,626.7億美元，<span style=\"color: red;\">至於8月份對華貿赤達<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">破紀錄386億美元</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32SOkAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32SOkAC.jpg&h=ac85c5cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2925c47e30f2ca51c2123f31da7b1fb67ddf0d82","tid":849202,"uid":143940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"證明 美國係入口&gt;出口"},{"pid":"abdbb4993d5ef4a0c74b7164088b799667117ddb","tid":849202,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e8336bd5858afde3da160d1e39f3083d2051f79","tid":849202,"uid":56459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"贏哂 唔驚啦"},{"pid":"ae7344f3af9307c14f03898cd2c7d97ca0c1295a","tid":849202,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國呢"},{"pid":"5b7216fd8c74a3c027e02c413f386af9e1a9a3f2","tid":849202,"uid":145496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"個個都趕加稅前入貨丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7486c4d0cd3a8b3af3cd11f7f35c7d16b8e03e0a","tid":849202,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi